CaWWzHCcGVEw">Tống Vi thập lục bình sự sung Đồng Cốc quận phòng ngự phán quan - 送韋十六評事充同谷郡防禦判官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-S%C6%B0-H%E1%BB%B1u/Tranh-nghinh-k%E1%BB%B3-l%C3%A3o/poem-NwIgEiGckyB8jsxKN30n4A">Tranh nghinh kỳ lão - 爭迎耆老</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-S%C6%B0-H%E1%BB%B1u/author-PX1pV4cjfZZCiPiOoAmgRg">Nguyễn Sư Hựu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-V%C4%83n-L%C3%BD/Trinh-li%E1%BB%87t-ch%C3%A2n-m%C3%A3nh-phu-nh%C3%A2n/poem-3AKknxw3RypvmfUnU-EPZA">Trinh liệt chân mãnh phu nhân - 貞烈真猛夫人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-V%C4%83n-L%C3%BD/author-06HpzLxTLc5w3aDHXJmyvw">Vũ Văn Lý</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-D%E1%BB%B1c-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/poem-TkW8fLOTmterjOmmEEwTBQ">Tương Dực đế - 襄翼帝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/author-1olZ3UNbr3C-_4X52NnUtA">Tự Đức hoàng đế</a>)<br></div>	</div>
